snippet.title: Avatar Raiders Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
This is an gameplay trailer of the upcomming Avatar Raiders wich will be available on steam shortly.
Avatar Raiders is an Overlay game for your Twitchstreams. Connect the game to your chat and let your viewers join in and kill some zombies.
See who lasts the longest.
